    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a factory-spec 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a pristine subframe with documented reinforcement. The high-revving S54 utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via an M-Variable Differential Lock. Meticulously maintained with recent rod bearing service and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul, this chassis remains incredibly rigid. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with an immaculate interior, this is a turn-key enthusiast piece optimized for both kinematics and aesthetics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
