      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece, preserved in a state that rivals its original showroom debut. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that is entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since day one. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, still carrying that distinct new-car scent, with every electronic component and high-tactile touchpoint functioning with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, housing a powertrain that has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy at authorized dealerships\u2014full service records are documented and included. With exceptionally low mileage and having been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in flawless, collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
