    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal cam timing. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally impeccable, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight, utilizing factory-spec bushings and dampers. The exterior retains its original paint depth with zero oxidation, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the purist seeking the ultimate high-revving driving experience.",
